description: This hall of fame Sakura purrs with a rating of 98, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 98, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, 5 for East, 3 for South, and Nine Lives for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [98 Votes, Hall of Fame]
